---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-4 pb-16 pt-8 md:px-8">
		<section class="mb-8 rounded-2xl border border-sky-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-50 via-white to-violet-50 p-6 md:p-8">
			<p class="mb-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-sky-700">About Me</p>
			<h1 class="mb-3 text-3xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-slate-900 md:text-4xl">경력과 교육 이수 내역</h1>
			<p class="text-slate-600">
				프론트엔드 개발 경험과 최근 AI/데이터 전문 교육 이수 내역을 정리했습니다.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="relative mb-8 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:p-8">
			<div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-500 to-violet-500"></div>
			<div class="mb-5 flex items-end justify-between gap-3">
				<h2 class="flex items-center gap-2 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">
					<span class="inline-block h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-sky-500"></span>
					경력사항
				</h2>
				<span class="rounded-full bg-sky-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-sky-800">총 4년</span>
			</div>
			<div class="overflow-x-auto">
				<table class="w-full min-w-[860px] border-collapse text-left">
					<thead>
						<tr class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-sky-50/70">
							<th class="px-3 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">재직 기간</th>
							<th class="px-3 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">회사명</th>
							<th class="px-3 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">부서 / 직급</th>
							<th class="px-3 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">담당 업무</th>
						</tr>
					</thead>
					<tbody>
						<tr class="border-b border-slate-100 align-top odd:bg-white even:bg-slate-50/60 transition-colors hover:bg-sky-50/60">
							<td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-slate-700">2021.06 ~ 2024.10</td>
							<td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-slate-900">(주) 반려생활</td>
							<td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-slate-700">개발팀 / 사원</td>
							<td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-slate-700">
								<ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 marker:text-sky-500">
									<li><a href="/projects/banlife-app" class="text-sky-500 hover:underline">반려생활 앱 프론트엔드 개발 담당 (React Native)</a></li>
									<li><a href="/projects/banlife-web" class="text-sky-500 hover:underline">반려생활 숙소 예약 웹 신규 프로젝트 기획 및 프론트엔드 개발 (Next.js)</a></li>
								</ul>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr class="align-top odd:bg-white even:bg-slate-50/60 transition-colors hover:bg-sky-50/60">
							<td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-slate-700">2021.02 ~ 2021.06</td>
							<td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-slate-900">(주) 헬로디지털</td>
							<td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-slate-700">개발팀 / 사원</td>
							<td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-slate-700">
								<ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 marker:text-sky-500">
									<li>React를 사용한 사내 어드민 웹사이트 외주 개발</li>
									<li>HTML, CSS, jQuery를 사용한 프로젝트 퍼블리싱 작업</li>
								</ul>
							</td>
						</tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:p-8">
			<div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-cyan-500"></div>
			<h2 class="mb-5 flex items-center gap-2 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">
				<span class="inline-block h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span>
				교육 이수
			</h2>
			<div class="overflow-x-auto">
				<table class="w-full min-w-[900px] border-collapse text-left">
					<thead>
						<tr class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-emerald-50/70">
							<th class="px-3 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">기간</th>
							<th class="px-3 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">기관명</th>
							<th class="px-3 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">교육명</th>
							<th class="px-3 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">상세 내용</th>
						</tr>
					</thead>
					<tbody>
						<tr class="align-top odd:bg-white even:bg-slate-50/60 transition-colors hover:bg-emerald-50/60">
							<td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-slate-700">2025.06 ~ 2026.01 (7개월)</td>
							<td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-slate-900">서울대학교</td>
							<td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-slate-700">SNU 빅데이터 핀테크 AI 고급 전문가 과정 - 11기</td>
							<td class="px-3 py-4 text-sm text-slate-700">
								<ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 marker:text-emerald-500">
									<li>총 1,040시간(교육 560시간, 프로젝트 실습 480시간)으로 진행됨</li>
									<li>AI 기술의 근본적인 이론부터 실제 프로젝트 실습까지 학습</li>
									<li>기업 연계 캡스톤 프로젝트 - '우수상' 수상
										<ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 marker:text-emerald-500">
											<li>1) <a href="/projects/capstone-3dgs-multi-agent-rag" class="text-emerald-500 hover:underline">K-MASA(Knowledge-grounded Multimodal Sales Agent)</a></li>
											<li>2) <a href="/projects/capstone-used-car-price-prediction" class="text-emerald-500 hover:underline">중고차 가격 예측 모델</a></li>
										</ul>
									</li>
								</ul>
							</td>
						</tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="mt-8 rounded-2xl border border-sky-200 bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-50 via-indigo-50 to-violet-50 p-6 text-center md:p-8">
			<p class="mb-2 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">연락처</p>
			<p class="mb-4 text-slate-600">협업이나 채용 관련 문의는 아래 이메일로 연락 부탁드립니다.</p>
			<a
				href="mailto:contact@taekim.dev"
				class="inline-flex items-center rounded-lg bg-slate-900 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-slate-800"
			>
				tae1344@gmail.com
			</a>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
